                     <interp inst="t18200217-52-person621" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am assistant to the Solicitor of the Mint. The shillings are both bad, and off the same die.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence I received it in change.</p>
